flowRoot.flowPara: Create arc diagrams for your favorite songs.
Head to your desktop to get started. (it's free)
Create arc diagrams for your favorite songs.
Leave That Thing Alone by Rush
It's free. There's no sign-in. Watch a clip.
First, let's separate the song into its parts by finding all the big transitions.
Now, let's match the parts that sound alike by dragging them into groups.
The last thing we'll do is split up each clip into small, repeated bits.
You can subdivide the clip into equal segments, or set transition points manually, then drag all the matching segments into a new group.
All the hard work's done! Now you can customize and download your arc chart.
